rong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">係全港性黎講，五大訴求已經講得好清楚，只要政府拒絕回應，做縮頭烏龜，民粹運動將會遍地開花！</span></strong><br />\n而係屯門區黎計，只要：<br />\n康文署無任何回應控制音響器材既時間表。<br />\n6/7當日未有解釋為何包庇疑犯使用胡椒噴霧，再放生。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">星期六屯門區遊行有近一萬人出席，但係第二日，班大媽都係照出返黎搵食！</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我真係好嬲！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">好啦後續行動</span></span></div><br />\n屯門區議會今個星期二(9/7)將會開所有人都齊既大會<br />\n當日所有親中派同埋官員代表都會出席<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">包括康文署</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">包括黑警</span><br />\n星期二(9/7)果日<span style=\"font-size: large;\">9:15</span>分就會正式開會<br />\n咁通常9:00會有人係示威區請願，官員呢就會早過9:00到，再落返黎接信<br />\n所以9:00前大家已經可以係示威區準備請願<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">好啦我地欣賞下政府既大樓先</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/07/07/0xFLYZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F07%2F07%2F0xFLYZ.png&h=c4a00d30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/07/07/St0sfo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F07%2F07%2FSt0sfo.png&h=c159e53e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n渣車既朋友可以泊架車係停車場，這是<span style=\"color: red;\">唯一</span>的出入口<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/07/07/wcxRzB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F07%2F07%2FwcxRzB.png&h=2e8d9688&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/07/07/oIXkg9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F07%2F07%2FoIXkg9.png&h=8c40de63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n示威區係圖中間，請願係<span style=\"color: red;\">無需要</span>不反對通知書<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/07/07/zXjvda.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F07%2F07%2FzXjvda.png&h=afcd460a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n紅線係可以人可以行去升降機大堂既路。<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/07/07/uq12Le.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F07%2F07%2Fuq12Le.jpg&h=0115a9b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/07/07/sF36dL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F07%2F07%2FsF36dL.jpg&h=4fd6e998&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n升降機大堂<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">只</span></span>有3架升降機<br />\n如果尊貴既親中議員，佢地無得坐升降機，要行樓梯就好慘<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.freeguider.com/upload/venues/1675/big/1d32d8593535de1b3e7fecedc8e1a74c.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.freeguider.com%2Fupload%2Fvenues%2F1675%2Fbig%2F1d32d8593535de1b3e7fecedc8e1a74c.JPG&h=d9a008b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n市民可以<span style=\"color: red;\">坐升降機</span>去一樓勞工處投訴老闆<br />\n市民可以<span style=\"color: red;\">坐升降機</span>去一樓社會福利署接受福利<br />\n市民可以<span style=\"color: red;\">坐升降機</span>去一樓入境處睇下自己張身分証<br />\n市民可以<span style=\"color: red;\">坐升降機</span>去二樓搵民政<br />\n市民可以<span style=\"color: red;\">坐升降機</span>去三樓<span style=\"color: red;\">會議室旁聽</span>(有步驟要做)<br />\n市民可以<span style=\"color: red;\">坐升降機</span>去五樓搵測量<br />\n市民可以<span style=\"color: red;\">坐升降機</span>去六樓搵地政了解親中議員有否違法掛BANNER<br />\n市民可以<span style=\"color: red;\">坐升降機</span>去七樓搵康文署(公園與遊樂場組)了解為何大媽問題沒有執法<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我無野講！我要請願！</span></div></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T17:57:18.000Z","msg":"巴打你係tg既邊個？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc18fb8f364c92e0932289e59903b19a9c306f10","tid":1293411,"uid":255497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T17:59:45.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"91bb1f4ebe671e1ff5902f18429f71e5d532e056","tid":1293411,"uid":255497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"q